{
  "id": "RAW_9caa8147",
  "title": "Vercel AI Gateway 现已支持 OpenResponses API - Vercel",
  "url": "https://vercel.com/changelog/openresponses-api-now-supported-on-vercel-ai-gateway",
  "date": "2026-01-15 13:00:00",
  "author": "Walter Korman, Rohan Taneja, Jerilyn Zheng",
  "siteName": "Vercel News",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <div data-customer-story=\"false\" class=\"flex flex-col items-center justify-start gap-6 flex-initial article-module__9eLiuW__content\">\n   <p class=\"text-copy-16 lg:text-copy-18 text-module__fl7lUq__paragraph\">Vercel AI Gateway is a day 0 launch partner for the OpenResponses API, an open-source specification from OpenAI for multi-provider AI interactions.</p>\n   <p class=\"text-copy-16 lg:text-copy-18 text-module__fl7lUq__paragraph\">OpenResponses provides a unified interface for text generation, streaming, tool calling, image input, and reasoning across providers.</p>\n   <p class=\"text-copy-16 lg:text-copy-18 text-module__fl7lUq__paragraph\"><b>AI Gateway supports OpenResponses for:</b></p>\n   <ul class=\"text-module__fl7lUq__unorderedList\">\n    <li class=\"text-copy-16 lg:text-copy-18 text-module__fl7lUq__paragraph text-module__fl7lUq__listItem\">\n     <p class=\"text-copy-16 lg:text-copy-18 text-module__fl7lUq__paragraph\"><b>Text generation:</b> Send messages and receive responses from any supported model.</p>\n    </li>\n    <li class=\"text-copy-16 lg:text-copy-18 text-module__fl7lUq__paragraph text-module__fl7lUq__listItem\">\n     <p class=\"text-copy-16 lg:text-copy-18 text-module__fl7lUq__paragraph\"><b>Streaming:</b> Receive tokens as they're generated via server-sent events.</p>\n    </li>\n    <li class=\"text-copy-16 lg:text-copy-18 text-module__fl7lUq__paragraph text-module__fl7lUq__listItem\">\n     <p class=\"text-copy-16 lg:text-copy-18 text-module__fl7lUq__paragraph\"><b>Tool calling:</b> Define functions that models can invoke with structured arguments.</p>\n    </li>\n    <li class=\"text-copy-16 lg:text-copy-18 text-module__fl7lUq__paragraph text-module__fl7lUq__listItem\">\n     <p class=\"text-copy-16 lg:text-copy-18 text-module__fl7lUq__paragraph\"><b>Image input:</b> Send images alongside text for vision-capable models.</p>\n    </li>\n    <li class=\"text-copy-16 lg:text-copy-18 text-module__fl7lUq__paragraph text-module__fl7lUq__listItem\">\n     <p class=\"text-copy-16 lg:text-copy-18 text-module__fl7lUq__paragraph\"><b>Reasoning:</b> Enable extended thinking with configurable effort levels.</p>\n    </li>\n    <li class=\"text-copy-16 lg:text-copy-18 text-module__fl7lUq__paragraph text-module__fl7lUq__listItem\">\n     <p class=\"text-copy-16 lg:text-copy-18 text-module__fl7lUq__paragraph\"><b>Provider fallbacks:</b> Configure automatic fallback chains across models and providers.</p>\n    </li>\n   </ul>\n   <p class=\"text-copy-16 lg:text-copy-18 text-module__fl7lUq__paragraph\">Use OpenResponses with your AI Gateway key, and switch models across providers by changing the model string.</p>\n   <div class=\"flex flex-col items-stretch justify-start gap-4 flex-initial blog-code-block-module__zaYDqW__wrapper\">\n    <div class=\"relative code-block-module__NOThwW__wrapper blog-code-block-module__zaYDqW__codeBlock\" data-geist-code-block=\"\">\n     <button aria-label=\"Copy code\" class=\"code-block-module__NOThwW__copyButton code-block-module__NOThwW__copyFloatingButton\" type=\"button\"></button>\n     <pre class=\"prism-code language-typescript code-block-module__NOThwW__pre blog-code-block-module__zaYDqW__maxHeight\"><code class=\"code-block-module__NOThwW__code\" data-geist-code-block=\"true\"><div class=\"line\" data-geist-code-block-line=\"true\" id=\"C347e45fc-L1\" style=\"font-feature-settings:&quot;liga&quot; off\"><div class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token keyword\">const</span><span class=\"token plain\"> response </span><span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token keyword\">await</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token function\">fetch</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'https://ai-gateway.vercel.sh/v1/responses'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token plain\"></span></div></div><div class=\"line\" data-geist-code-block-line=\"true\" id=\"C347e45fc-L2\" style=\"font-feature-settings:&quot;liga&quot; off\"><div class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token plain\">  method</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token string\">'POST'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token plain\"></span></div></div><div class=\"line\" data-geist-code-block-line=\"true\" id=\"C347e45fc-L3\" style=\"font-feature-settings:&quot;liga&quot; off\"><div class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token plain\">  headers</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token plain\"></span></div></div><div class=\"line\" data-geist-code-block-line=\"true\" id=\"C347e45fc-L4\" style=\"font-feature-settings:&quot;liga&quot; off\"><div class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token plain\">    </span><span class=\"token string-property property\">'Content-Type'</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token string\">'application/json'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token plain\"></span></div></div><div class=\"line\" data-geist-code-block-line=\"true\" id=\"C347e45fc-L5\" style=\"font-feature-settings:&quot;liga&quot; off\"><div class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token plain\">    Authorization</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token template-string template-punctuation string\">`</span><span class=\"token template-string string\">Bearer </span><span class=\"token template-string interpolation interpolation-punctuation punctuation\">${</span><span class=\"token template-string interpolation\">process</span><span class=\"token template-string interpolation punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token template-string interpolation\">env</span><span class=\"token template-string interpolation punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token template-string interpolation constant\">VERCEL_AI_GATEWAY_KEY</span><span class=\"token template-string interpolation interpolation-punctuation punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token template-string template-punctuation string\">`</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token plain\"></span></div></div><div class=\"line\" data-geist-code-block-line=\"true\" id=\"C347e45fc-L6\" style=\"font-feature-settings:&quot;liga&quot; off\"><div class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token plain\">  </span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token plain\"></span></div></div><div class=\"line\" data-geist-code-block-line=\"true\" id=\"C347e45fc-L7\" style=\"font-feature-settings:&quot;liga&quot; off\"><div class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token plain\">  body</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token constant\">JSON</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">stringify</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token plain\"></span></div></div><div class=\"line\" data-geist-code-block-line=\"true\" id=\"C347e45fc-L8\" style=\"font-feature-settings:&quot;liga&quot; off\"><div class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token plain\">    model</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token string\">'anthropic/claude-sonnet-4.5'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token plain\"></span></div></div><div class=\"line\" data-geist-code-block-line=\"true\" id=\"C347e45fc-L9\" style=\"font-feature-settings:&quot;liga&quot; off\"><div class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token plain\">    input</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token plain\"></span></div></div><div class=\"line\" data-geist-code-block-line=\"true\" id=\"C347e45fc-L10\" style=\"font-feature-settings:&quot;liga&quot; off\"><div class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token plain\">      </span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token plain\"></span></div></div><div class=\"line\" data-geist-code-block-line=\"true\" id=\"C347e45fc-L11\" style=\"font-feature-settings:&quot;liga&quot; off\"><div class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token plain\">        type</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token string\">'message'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token plain\"></span></div></div><div class=\"line\" data-geist-code-block-line=\"true\" id=\"C347e45fc-L12\" style=\"font-feature-settings:&quot;liga&quot; off\"><div class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token plain\">        role</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token string\">'user'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token plain\"></span></div></div><div class=\"line\" data-geist-code-block-line=\"true\" id=\"C347e45fc-L13\" style=\"font-feature-settings:&quot;liga&quot; off\"><div class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token plain\">        content</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token string\">'Explain quantum computing in one sentence.'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token plain\"></span></div></div><div class=\"line\" data-geist-code-block-line=\"true\" id=\"C347e45fc-L14\" style=\"font-feature-settings:&quot;liga&quot; off\"><div class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token plain\">      </span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token plain\"></span></div></div><div class=\"line\" data-geist-code-block-line=\"true\" id=\"C347e45fc-L15\" style=\"font-feature-settings:&quot;liga&quot; off\"><div class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token plain\">    </span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token plain\"></span></div></div><div class=\"line\" data-geist-code-block-line=\"true\" id=\"C347e45fc-L16\" style=\"font-feature-settings:&quot;liga&quot; off\"><div class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token plain\">  </span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token plain\"></span></div></div><div class=\"line\" data-geist-code-block-line=\"true\" id=\"C347e45fc-L17\" style=\"font-feature-settings:&quot;liga&quot; off\"><div class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token plain\"></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></div></div></code></pre>\n    </div>\n    <p class=\"text-center text-copy-14 text-gray-900\"></p>\n   </div>\n   <p class=\"text-copy-16 lg:text-copy-18 text-module__fl7lUq__paragraph\">You can also use OpenResponses for more complex cases, like tool calling.</p>\n   <div class=\"flex flex-col items-stretch justify-start gap-4 flex-initial blog-code-block-module__zaYDqW__wrapper\">\n    <div class=\"relative code-block-module__NOThwW__wrapper blog-code-block-module__zaYDqW__codeBlock\" data-geist-code-block=\"\">\n     <button aria-label=\"Copy code\" class=\"code-block-module__NOThwW__copyButton code-block-module__NOThwW__copyFloatingButton\" type=\"button\"></button>\n     <pre class=\"prism-code language-typescript code-block-module__NOThwW__pre blog-code-block-module__zaYDqW__maxHeight\"><code class=\"code-block-module__NOThwW__code\" data-geist-code-block=\"true\"><div class=\"line\" data-geist-code-block-line=\"true\" id=\"C39d5b57f-L1\" style=\"font-feature-settings:&quot;liga&quot; off\"><div class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token keyword\">const</span><span class=\"token plain\"> response </span><span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token keyword\">await</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token function\">fetch</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'https://ai-gateway.vercel.sh/v1/responses'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token plain\"></span></div></div><div class=\"line\" data-geist-code-block-line=\"true\" id=\"C39d5b57f-L2\" style=\"font-feature-settings:&quot;liga&quot; off\"><div class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token plain\">  method</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token string\">'POST'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token plain\"></span></div></div><div class=\"line\" data-geist-code-block-line=\"true\" id=\"C39d5b57f-L3\" style=\"font-feature-settings:&quot;liga&quot; off\"><div class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token plain\">  headers</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token plain\"></span></div></div><div class=\"line\" data-geist-code-block-line=\"true\" id=\"C39d5b57f-L4\" style=\"font-feature-settings:&quot;liga&quot; off\"><div class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token plain\">    </span><span class=\"token string-property property\">'Content-Type'</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token string\">'application/json'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token plain\"></span></div></div><div class=\"line\" data-geist-code-block-line=\"true\" id=\"C39d5b57f-L5\" style=\"font-feature-settings:&quot;liga&quot; off\"><div class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token plain\">    Authorization</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token template-string template-punctuation string\">`</span><span class=\"token template-string string\">Bearer </span><span class=\"token template-string interpolation interpolation-punctuation punctuation\">${</span><span class=\"token template-string interpolation\">process</span><span class=\"token template-string interpolation punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token template-string interpolation\">env</span><span class=\"token template-string interpolation punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token template-string interpolation constant\">VERCEL_AI_GATEWAY_KEY</span><span class=\"token template-string interpolation interpolation-punctuation punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token template-string template-punctuation string\">`</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token plain\"></span></div></div><div class=\"line\" data-geist-code-block-line=\"true\" id=\"C39d5b57f-L6\" style=\"font-feature-settings:&quot;liga&quot; off\"><div class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token plain\">  </span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token plain\"></span></div></div><div class=\"line\" data-geist-code-block-line=\"true\" id=\"C39d5b57f-L7\" style=\"font-feature-settings:&quot;liga&quot; off\"><div class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token plain\">  body</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token constant\">JSON</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">stringify</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token plain\"></span></div></div><div class=\"line\" data-geist-code-block-line=\"true\" id=\"C39d5b57f-L8\" style=\"font-feature-settings:&quot;liga&quot; off\"><div class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token plain\">    model</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token string\">'zai/glm-4.7'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token plain\"></span></div></div><div class=\"line\" data-geist-code-block-line=\"true\" id=\"C39d5b57f-L9\" style=\"font-feature-settings:&quot;liga&quot; off\"><div class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token plain\">    input</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token plain\"> type</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token string\">'message'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token plain\"> role</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token string\">'user'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token plain\"> content</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token string\">'What is the weather in SF?'</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token plain\"></span></div></div><div class=\"line\" data-geist-code-block-line=\"true\" id=\"C39d5b57f-L10\" style=\"font-feature-settings:&quot;liga&quot; off\"><div class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token plain\">    tools</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token plain\"></span></div></div><div class=\"line\" data-geist-code-block-line=\"true\" id=\"C39d5b57f-L11\" style=\"font-feature-settings:&quot;liga&quot; off\"><div class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token plain\">      type</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token string\">'function'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token plain\"></span></div></div><div class=\"line\" data-geist-code-block-line=\"true\" id=\"C39d5b57f-L12\" style=\"font-feature-settings:&quot;liga&quot; off\"><div class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token plain\">      name</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token string\">'get_weather'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token plain\"></span></div></div><div class=\"line\" data-geist-code-block-line=\"true\" id=\"C39d5b57f-L13\" style=\"font-feature-settings:&quot;liga&quot; off\"><div class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token plain\">      description</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token string\">'Get current weather for a location'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token plain\"></span></div></div><div class=\"line\" data-geist-code-block-line=\"true\" id=\"C39d5b57f-L14\" style=\"font-feature-settings:&quot;liga&quot; off\"><div class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token plain\">      parameters</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token plain\"></span></div></div><div class=\"line\" data-geist-code-block-line=\"true\" id=\"C39d5b57f-L15\" style=\"font-feature-settings:&quot;liga&quot; off\"><div class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token plain\">        type</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token string\">'object'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token plain\"></span></div></div><div class=\"line\" data-geist-code-block-line=\"true\" id=\"C39d5b57f-L16\" style=\"font-feature-settings:&quot;liga&quot; off\"><div class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token plain\">        properties</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token plain\"> location</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token plain\"> type</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token string\">'string'</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token plain\"></span></div></div><div class=\"line\" data-geist-code-block-line=\"true\" id=\"C39d5b57f-L17\" style=\"font-feature-settings:&quot;liga&quot; off\"><div class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token plain\">        required</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token string\">'location'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token plain\"></span></div></div><div class=\"line\" data-geist-code-block-line=\"true\" id=\"C39d5b57f-L18\" style=\"font-feature-settings:&quot;liga&quot; off\"><div class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token plain\">      </span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token plain\"></span></div></div><div class=\"line\" data-geist-code-block-line=\"true\" id=\"C39d5b57f-L19\" style=\"font-feature-settings:&quot;liga&quot; off\"><div class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token plain\">    </span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token plain\"></span></div></div><div class=\"line\" data-geist-code-block-line=\"true\" id=\"C39d5b57f-L20\" style=\"font-feature-settings:&quot;liga&quot; off\"><div class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token plain\">  </span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token plain\"></span></div></div><div class=\"line\" data-geist-code-block-line=\"true\" id=\"C39d5b57f-L21\" style=\"font-feature-settings:&quot;liga&quot; off\"><div class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token plain\"></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></div></div></code></pre>\n    </div>\n    <p class=\"text-center text-copy-14 text-gray-900\"></p>\n   </div>\n   <p class=\"text-copy-16 lg:text-copy-18 text-module__fl7lUq__paragraph\">Read the <a href=\"https://vercel.com/docs/ai-gateway/openresponses\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_self\" data-track=\"true\" data-track-click-name=\"article_link\" data-track-click-value=\"https://vercel.com/docs/ai-gateway/openresponses\" data-zone=\"null\" class=\"link-module__Q1NRQq__link link-module__Q1NRQq__highlight [&amp;_u]:no-underline\">OpenResponses API documentation</a> or <a href=\"https://www.openresponses.org/specification\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\" data-track=\"true\" data-track-click-name=\"article_link\" data-track-click-value=\"https://www.openresponses.org/specification\" data-zone=\"null\" class=\"link-module__Q1NRQq__link link-module__Q1NRQq__highlight [&amp;_u]:no-underline\">view the specification</a>.</p>\n  </div>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "Vercel AI Gateway 现已集成 OpenResponses API，这是 OpenAI 的开源规范，为多提供商 AI 交互（如文本生成、流式传输、工具调用和图像输入）提供统一接口。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "Vercel AI Gateway 现已集成 OpenResponses API，这是 OpenAI 的开源规范，为多提供商 AI 交互（如文本生成、流式传输、工具调用和图像输入）提供统一接口。",
  "summary": "Vercel 宣布其 AI Gateway 成为 OpenResponses API 的 day-0 发布合作伙伴，这是 OpenAI 设计的开源规范，旨在标准化跨多个提供商的 AI 交互。此集成为开发者提供了统一接口来处理各种 AI 功能，包括文本生成、令牌的实时流式传输、带结构化参数的复杂工具调用，以及面向视觉模型的图像输入。该 API 还支持可配置工作量的高级推理，并提供提供商回退链以增强可靠性。开发者可以利用其现有的 AI Gateway 密钥，通过简单地更改请求中的模型字符串，在不同 AI 模型和提供商之间无缝切换，通过单一端点简化多样化 AI 生态系统的管理。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "Vercel AI Gateway 现支持 OpenResponses API，实现统一的 AI 交互。",
      "explanation": "此集成允许开发者通过 Vercel 的 AI Gateway 使用单一接口访问不同提供商的各种 AI 服务（文本、流式传输、工具调用、图像输入）。"
    },
    {
      "point": "OpenResponses API 标准化了多提供商 AI 功能。",
      "explanation": "该 API 是 OpenAI 的开源规范，为常见任务（如文本生成、工具调用和流式传输）与多样化 AI 模型交互提供了一致的方式。"
    },
    {
      "point": "它提供诸如提供商回退和可配置推理级别等功能。",
